The apparent permselectivity of the membrane is one of the most important parameters for an IEM. This figure of merit was used to define the best-performing material among the ones under study. In literature, the apparent permselectivity of the membrane can be calculated with or without the ion transport numbers of the ions in the solution36,59. In this study, both will be calculated to be comparable to what has been previously done.1αap=EmemEthe.\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
